                    <h1 class="domdom">27</h1>

                    <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/714"> Film For Holocaust Memorial Day: Paragraph 175 (2000)</a></h1>

                    <h2>27 Jan 2011, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                    <p>Under Paragraph 175 of the 1871 Germal penal code sodomy was a criminal offence.  From 1935 onwards the Nazi regime used it to incarcerate gay men in the concentration camp system as social undesirables. Five survivors of the camps tell their stories.</p>

                    <p class="viewlink"><a href="/on/film/714">Read More &raquo;</a></p>

